Revision history for Perl extension LXRT.

0.01  Mon Jan 10 14:28:31 2000
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.18
0.02  Wed Mar 15 17:37:00 2000
	- updated to work with RTAI 1.2, not backward compatible
	- automatically installs a version.h file in ../../include
	- automatically installs rtai/rtai_sched when loading LXRT.pm

0.03  Thu May  3 15:26:05 EDT 2001 pcloutier@PoseidonControls.com
	- Ported to RTAI-2.4.3.
	- Fixed num2nam().
	- Verified returned pointers are ok.
	- Added rt_agent() and semaphore functions.
	- Adding the other functions should be trivial.
